OL,7,FTwo men who stole thousands of pounds
OL,8,Ffrom supermarkets and petrol stations
OL,9,Facross Kent in a series of ram raids
OL,10,Fhave been ordered to repay more than
OL,11,F#120,000.
OL,13,FAnthony Pemberthy and Stephen
OL,14,FDavenport, both from Maidstone, were
OL,15,Fmembers of a group that targeted six
OL,16,Fbusinesses between 2019 and 2021.
OL,18,FThey used diggers to try and remove
OL,19,Fcash machines in Cranbrook,
OL,20,FStaplehurst, Whitfield, Northfleet,
OL,21,FDymchurch and Dargate.
