OL,7,FIn November 2022, Pemberthy was given
OL,8,Fan eight-year and nine-month sentence
OL,9,Ffor six offences, and Davenport was
OL,10,Fhanded seven years and five months for
OL,11,Ftwo offences.
OL,13,FA hearing on Thursday 31 October
OL,14,Fordered the men to pay the money in
OL,15,Fthe next three months.
OL,17,FPemberthy, 46, was ordered to pay back
OL,18,F#108,000 and Davenport, 63, was
OL,19,Fordered to pay #14,300.
