OL,7,FIf they fail to comply, they will
OL,8,Fserve extra time in prison.
OL,10,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,11,FSuperintendent Chris Greenstreet said:
OL,12,F"These offences not only had a big
OL,13,Fimpact on the businesses targeted,
OL,14,Fboth in terms of the money stolen and
OL,15,Fthe damage done to buildings, but also
OL,16,Fon the wider community who weren't
OL,17,Fable to access essential services.
